metadata.name: The Ghost Rider
metadata.description:
This 1/1 continues the story of the superhero Method Man as he rides out of Wu-York city in his pursuit of justice.

Designed and animated by Jonathan Winbush with story concept direction by Ray Acosta and Method Man

About MEFaverse:
The MEFaverse, starring legendary Hip Hop artist and award-winning actor, Method Man has officially landed. Only in this iteration, Method Man is a superhero.
